## Capture Summary

Media assets have been successfully captured for the art print storefront demo using Playwright deterministic screenshots and screen recording.

### Capture Command
```bash
node scripts/capture.mjs \
  --url "http://localhost:5173/public/demos/art-print-storefront/" \
  --slug "art-print-storefront" \
  --out "upwork-runs/let-s-create-this-shopify/proposal/media" \
  --flow "upwork-runs/let-s-create-this-shopify/capture-flow.json"
```

